Onevent BEFORE_AREA Gosub AV_DATREG From W1CPYLEGUKI
Return

$AV_DATREG
Chgfmt [M]DATREG(indice) With "D:"+GFMDAT
Gosub _AFF
Return

Subprog C_DATREG(VALEUR)
Variable Date    VALEUR
## Action %OBLIG
If VALEUR=[0/0/0]
 mkstat = 1 : GMESSAGE = mess(10,123,1)
Endif
If mkstat : GERR = 1 : GZONE = "DATREG" : GZNUM = 1001873 : Endif
